### Backend API Testing File
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4001
@token = YOUR_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check (if you add this endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ============================================
### AUTHENTICATION REQUIRED ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Users (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Pending Teachers (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/pending-teachers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Statistics (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Students (Teacher/Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Subjects
GET {{baseUrl}}/subjects

### ============================================
### ADMIN ACTIONS
### ============================================

### Approve Teacher
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/approve-teacher/APPROVAL_TOKEN_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete User
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### TEACHER ACTIONS
### ============================================

### Register as Teacher
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register-teacher
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### GRADES
### ============================================

### Get Grades (Teacher/Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/grades
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Grade (Teacher/Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/grades
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "student_firebase_uid",
  "subject": "subject_name",
  "knowledge": {
    "exercise": 80,
    "flowchart": 85
  },
  "skills": {
    "reading": 75,
    "planning": 80,
    "equipmentUsage": 85,
    "problemSolving": 90,
    "improvement": 75,
    "programming": 85,
    "presentation": 80,
    "attitude": 90
  }
}

### ============================================
### FILES
### ============================================

### Get Folders
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/folders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get User Files
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/user/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### SCHEDULES
### ============================================

### Get Teacher Schedule
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedules/TEACHER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create/Update Schedule
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "day": "monday",
  "timeSlot": "10:00-12:00",
  "subject": "subject_name"
}




